  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK261">
<l>uṟṟanōy nōṉṟa luyirkkuṟukaṇ ceyyāmai</l>
<l>yaṟṟē tavattiṟ kuru</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The nature of religious discipline consists, in the endurance (by the ascetic) of the sufferings which it brings on himself, and in abstaining from giving pain to others.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
